PLEASE LEAVE YOUR COMMENTS

Personally i love this map i think its the best one ive made yet, simply because you can do so many tricks on it =P. Heres a clue if your gonna play it, go round top once without stopping to get speed then flick round to the surf that goes up to top, as your going on the surf to top again flick up and jump out of the push zone and youll get alot of height, you might even find a buyzone. Theres a few secret areas in the map which are pretty easy to get to as there all in the same place =P. Well i hope you enjoy this map as i did.
